Assyrian Church of the East: Europe (Norsborg, Sweden); Canada (Weston, Ontario); Eastern USA (Chicago; residence of the
Patr. patr.
), Western USA (Glendale, Arizona); Western California (San Jose); Australia and New Zealand (Sydney). With communities in several other countries, including Denmark, Germany, Great Britian, Greece, and Russia. Whereas some 150,000 now live in the Diaspora (ca. 90,000 in USA, and 10,000 in Australia/New Zealand), only ca. 100,000 remain in the Middle East.
